<div id="info"> 
  <p> The EIK distance laboratory system i-Tee offers labs for different courses.</p>
  <ol>
    <li> Log in the system with a EIK class username and password.</li>
    <li> Choose a lab</li>
    <li> Start the lab and read trough the given materials.</li>
    <li> End the lab once you're done (or save it to continue later)</li>
  </ol>
  <p> Please refer to Margus Ernits if you have any questions. The e-mail address can be found in the Studies Information System (OIS)</p>
</div>
<div id="sign_in">
  
  <h2>Sign in</h2>

<%= form_for(resource, :as => resource_name, :url => session_path(resource_name)) do |f| %>
  <p><%= f.label :username %><br />
  <%= f.text_field :username %></p>

  <p><%= f.label :password %><br />
  <%= f.password_field :password %></p>

<%# if devise_mapping.rememberable? -%>
<%#= f.check_box :remember_me %> <%#= f.label :remember_me %> 
  <%# end -%>
  
  <p><%= f.submit "Sign in" %></p>
<% end %>
</div>
